    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Software Engineer to strengthen our Nagpur-based team.\n\nAbout Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates:\nNewgen Software Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates!",
